name: ATO-Philippines, Inc. Official Coat of Arms

desc.html: ALPHA TAU OMEGA-PHILIPPINES, INC. was Founded on August 15, 1968 as International Christian Service Fraternal Organization. There were six (6) Founders namely; Manuel M. Momongan, Manolito J. Mangubat, Rolando C. Marigomen, Raul C. Murillo, Wilfredo R. Ursal and Jesus D. Flores

wiki.Credit: Alpha Tau Omega was created when it severed its relationshio with Alpha Sigma Phi as a sign of protest when Alpha Sigma Phi-Silliman University initiated a merging with a fraternity with a dubious history, the Alpha Sigma Phi-Central Mindanao University.
